      </h2>
    </div>
    <p
      id="main-text"
      class="text-wrap max-w-4xl text-center text-base lg:text-lg"
    >
      hii im snowy, your average amateur anime degenerate!!
      <br />
      i like to watch anime, play games, and code in my free time.
      <br />
